                    "message": {
                        "text": "FinancialPoolManager.payInstallment(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#201-270) uses timestamp for comparisons\n\tDangerous comparisons:\n\t- require(bool,string)(keccak256(bytes)(bytes(pool.status)) == keccak256(bytes)(bytes(active)),Pool is not active) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#204-207)\n\t- require(bool,string)(msg.value == pool.installmentValue,Incorrect installment value) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#219)\n\t- block.timestamp > pool.activationDate (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#223)\n\t- duePayments > pool.installments (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#226)\n\t- require(bool,string)(participant.payments < duePayments + 1,Too many payments made) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#232)\n\t- require(bool,string)(participant.payments < pool.installments,All installments already paid) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#233)\n\t- participant.payments == duePayments && ! participant.received (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#241)\n"
